{"tid":2140990,"cid":5,"subCid":11,"title":"保安局強烈譴責有人發放虛假信息","createTime":"2020-08-05T11:05:57.000Z","updateTime":"2020-08-05T20:31:13.000Z","uid":240362,"like":39,"dislike":175,"uniUserReply":114,"replies":[{"pid":"1f860ce47c608f4d51acd93f70a4e105a156dd91","tid":2140990,"uid":240362,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":2,"replyTime":"2020-08-05T11:05:57.000Z","msg":"<a href=\"https://www.info.gov.hk/gia/general/202008/05/P2020080500615.htm\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fwww.info.gov.hk%2Fgia%2Fgeneral%2F202008%2F05%2FP2020080500615.htm&d=Iz1eZ%2FSDqTYQUikxH7ZeatMQoCHxbgs64DeXVNsql00%3D&h=bcce7b52\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://www.info.gov.hk/gia/general/202008/05/P2020080500615.htm</a><br />\n<br />\n保安局強烈譴責有人發放虛假信息<br />\n＊＊＊＊＊＊＊＊＊＊＊＊＊＊＊<br />\n  保安局留意到今日（八月五日）有人在社交媒體發放虛假信息，誤導市民指保安局局長曾發表政府會對干預香港事務的國家的外交人員及其在港僑民進行拘捕或懲處的言論。<br />\n<br />\n  保安局發言人表示，這是虛假信息，企圖製造事端，對用心不良發放虛假信息的行為予以強烈譴責。<br />\n <br />\n完<br />\n2020年8月5日（星期三）<br />\n香港時間18時56分"},{"pid":"93fd6b44d64646d241c54cebbb841b19b53ce35a","tid":2140990,"uid":132587,"like":142,"dislike":1,"score":141,"citedBy":3,"replyTime":"2020-08-05T11:06:47.000Z","msg":"此回覆已被刪除"},{"pid":"e855e4c83ae2098dc0bfc76d797128e2f3bfe3a4","tid":2140990,"uid":240362,"like":7,"dislike":0,"score":7,"quote":{"pid":"93fd6b44d64646d241c54cebbb841b19b53ce35a","tid":2140990,"uid":132587,"like":142,"dislike":1,"score":141,"citedBy":3,"replyTime":"2020-08-05T11:06:47.000Z","msg":"此回覆已被刪除"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-08-05T11:06:57.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/haha.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/haha.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/haha.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/haha.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/haha.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"b556736dd73d0f1e1ff252e11a15cbc5c6309498","tid":2140990,"uid":49329,"like":7,"dislike":0,"score":7,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-08-05T11:08:24.000Z","msg